      • DefaultHomeInputStream

        public DefaultHomeInputStream(InputStream in,
                              ContentRecording contentRecording,
                              UserPreferences preferences,
                              boolean preferPreferencesContent)
        Creates a home input stream filter able to read a home and its content from in. If preferences isn't null and preferPreferencesContent is true, the furniture and textures contents it references will replace the one of the read home when they are equal. If preferPreferencesContent is false, preferences content will be used only to replace damaged equal content that might be found in read home files.
